headline: Ford CEO Jim Farley says skilled labor shortage holds back 'made in America' ambitions
summary: Ford CEO Jim Farley is bullish on President Trump's drive for more US-made products. But there might not be enough skilled workers to service the spike in demand, let alone build the new plants.
